{"id":287223,"date":[{"year":1953,"month":6,"day":8}],"page":"7","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"文化广场","column":"波兰民歌","genre":"","count":"98","ytitle":"","mtitle":"“农村姑娘”","ftitle":"(克林波夫古老的民歌)","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"(这首歌是姑娘们在田里辛苦工作着的时候唱的。)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你快下山吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是这样的疲劳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的手脚都酸痛了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要是你也像我们一样的辛劳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那你早就下山了。"}]}